{"tid":2185182,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不滿便衣警挑釁踩文宣 56歲護理員認襲擊囚兩個月 潘敏琦駁回上訴：係咪要學日本武士道打人","createTime":"2020-09-02T05:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T08:36:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"2342ff76ee84986ea624b01298aa95afad1edac9","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"市民去年10月1日在港鐵太子站外將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在地上，其間有便衣警上前挑釁，將何的相片「踢甩」。在場貼文宣的女護理員見狀感不滿，用手中塗抹漿糊的長棍打了便衣警一下，她早前承認普通襲擊罪，判監兩個月，准保釋等候上訴。高院法官潘敏琦今駁回申請，護理員須即時服刑。<strong><span class=\"red\">潘官指被告千里迢迢到太子貼文宣，若說預計不到會遭人指罵或刺激到別人，「呢個陳詞太幼稚喇」</span></strong>；她又質疑即使別人踢走文宣，被告是否就要以「日本武士道」的動作，猛力揮動鋁棒打對方。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前求情指，被告蔡妙兒（56歲）不滿便衣警羅國威踩爛地上海報和粗言指罵，一時衝動犯案；並透露被告患病，左腳行動不便，需要長期服藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2F2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4b4e754c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2F2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI%2F&h=c3d2f147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI/</a>"},{"pid":"a02bf7ebded1a3237bd484ac7d2a2511b849cffc","tid":2185182,"uid":145117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"594d4ce38dbb02d52020207983595fa2cf9845aa","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":43,"score":-37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"潘敏琦並謂，「法官同裁判官不是住喺象牙之塔」，會知道社會氛圍；質疑被告千里迢迢由屯門去到太子站貼文宣，「如果話預計唔到有人指罵、刺激到人哋，呢個陳詞太幼稚喇。」"},{"pid":"54bc55362e3b98038c19a0ae1114a1996f9a4f43","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a02bf7ebded1a3237bd484ac7d2a2511b849cffc","tid":2185182,"uid":145117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc782da6b80dfba9ad3b090879a179e8c958028d","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":27,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">上訴指警挑釁在先 官：我唔知</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n辯方指出片中有人踢走地上文宣，潘官反駁：「係呀，咁就要俾人打㗎嗱？」潘官形容片段拍到被告從一段距離外衝前，如「日本武士道」般高舉85厘米長鋁杆，從上而下猛力打落事主身上。上訴方澄清指，並非說被告行為正確合理，但強調片段開始前已有事發生；惟<strong><span class=\"red\">法官表示不猜測片段以外之事，「我唔知，我淨係見到有人舉步維艱」，即日駁回上訴，將另擇日子頒下判詞。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a08d9b807cef75c3362010859f6e1824e283e641","tid":2185182,"uid":145117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54bc55362e3b98038c19a0ae1114a1996f9a4f43","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a02bf7ebded1a3237bd484ac7d2a2511b849cffc","tid":2185182,"uid":145117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/