2185182,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"武士道：<br />\n<br />\n明治維新前是武士階層既生活準則<br />\n<br />\n明治維新後，武士階層消失，武士道化為日本國民既道德、風氣、習慣等，成為民族精神中重要既一部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpXvfQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpXvfQE.jpg&h=59c1f0c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2baa2dca85d2b961fceafdea95ad46cf5b7b5de4","tid":2185182,"uid":132256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2342ff76ee84986ea624b01298aa95afad1edac9","tid":2185182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"市民去年10月1日在港鐵太子站外將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在地上，其間有便衣警上前挑釁，將何的相片「踢甩」。在場貼文宣的女護理員見狀感不滿，用手中塗抹漿糊的長棍打了便衣警一下，她早前承認普通襲擊罪，判監兩個月，准保釋等候上訴。高院法官潘敏琦今駁回申請，護理員須即時服刑。<strong><span class=\"red\">潘官指被告千里迢迢到太子貼文宣，若說預計不到會遭人指罵或刺激到別人，「呢個陳詞太幼稚喇」</span></strong>；她又質疑即使別人踢走文宣，被告是否就要以「日本武士道」的動作，猛力揮動鋁棒打對方。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前求情指，被告蔡妙兒（56歲）不滿便衣警羅國威踩爛地上海報和粗言指罵，一時衝動犯案；並透露被告患病，左腳行動不便，需要長期服藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2F2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4b4e754c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2F2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI%2F&h=c3d2f147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/2MBISCJRR5DWDCCQLMCPNWWRGI/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"咪睇你哋惡得幾耐 共慘黨保你唔到㗎 法官大人"},{"pid":"38a597534fc8ad1f585ce493bfe82f6f38b336aa","tid":2185182,"uid":184216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"呢個咁嘅閪官同陳百祥有咩撚野分別"},{"pid":"906020f46565362dd4657ae0d04adf51c5c713a2","tid":2185182,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig